body:
The Strangest Strategy

So, I’ve been using Google Docs lately (which has been a darling; ironic, given Google usually being Satan incarnate) to store a bunch of my writings. But just recently, I decided to use it, instead of Tumblr, to write out the Wedding. I don’t know how, but it’s been working like a charm. I already got the first two parts knocked out already. Probably gonna wait until writing Part 3, before I begin posting them, to save on people waiting on them.

On a related note, I think I’m gonna need help from an artist for something. I want to include illustrated wedding photos of Retsuko, Haida, Ikari, the families, some friends, etc., to put in…I’m thinking the epilogue. If you happen to know anyone who can pull it off, and might be interested, PM me, or mention them, or whatever you want.
